My goal is to work with the Division of Family and Children Services to help children who have been hurt or neglected. I also want to help families who are having problems. Important values that I can bring to this job are service, respect, and a strong sense of what is right and wrong. I want to help people get along better and to be the best person I can be in my job.

I have always wanted to help others. But I was not sure what kind of work I wanted to do. In high school and college, I saw people who were unhappy and dealing with problems in bad ways. Because of what I saw, I chose to study psychology. After I finished college in 2009, I took some time off. One day, I visited a friend who had a 16-year-old boy visiting her. He was there because he was escaping his parents who were being mean to him. The next day, I went to the boy's parents' house to talk to them. I told the police about my concerns because I had recently finished college and studied psychology. The police asked me to talk to the parents. When I talked to them, they seemed nervous and made excuses for their behavior. After this, I decided that I wanted to help children who have problems like this.

Another important value for me is fairness. We say that each person is special and we are sad when someone dies. But we also want to be like everyone else. I am a special person and I do not like to be limited by what others think. In high school and college, I fought against unfairness whenever I could. I wore clothes that showed my personality, made my hair different colors, and spoke out against racism and unfairness. I believe in being fair and I will continue to fight for what is right.

This paper looks at the Biological and Sociocultural models of a sleep problem called insomnia. Insomnia is a sleep disorder. There are two main ways to look at this problem: the Biological model and the Sociocultural model. The Biological model looks at genetics and health. The Sociocultural model looks at how the environment and things like race, ethnicity, and income affect sleep.

Insomnia is a sleep problem. It can be caused by many things, including other mental health problems, medical conditions, or substances. There are many types of sleep problems. Some are called Dyssomnias, which are problems with falling asleep or staying asleep. Others are called Parasomnias, which are problems with strange behaviors during sleep.

Dyssomnias include insomnia, which is a problem falling asleep or staying asleep. Hypersomnia is a problem staying awake. Narcolepsy is a problem with staying awake and alert. Breathing-related sleep disorder and circadian rhythm sleep disorder are other types of Dyssomnias. The biological model says that genetics and health can cause these problems.

One study looked at mice to understand how genes affect sleep. The study found that certain receptors in the brain help control sleep and wakefulness. These receptors can be affected by genetics, which can cause sleep problems. This study shows that genetics can affect sleep, which is good to know for people with insomnia.

The Sociocultural model looks at how the environment and society affect sleep. For example, people from different cultures or with different incomes may have different sleep patterns. A study found that certain genetic receptors in the brain can be affected by genetics, which can cause sleep problems. This means that people with certain genetic traits may have trouble sleeping.

This study is important because it shows that genetics can affect sleep. If people have a genetic problem that affects sleep, it can make it hard for them to focus and do daily tasks. This can affect their lives in many ways.

This paper is about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). We will explain what CAPD is, how it is diagnosed, and ways a teacher can help a student with CAPD in a classroom.

CAPD is a disorder of the brain. It means the brain has trouble understanding what we hear. People with CAPD can hear sounds, but their brain does not work correctly to understand them. This is not the same as being deaf. A person with CAPD can hear normally, but their brain has trouble separating different sounds or understanding what is being said.

The idea of CAPD was first discovered in the 1950s. Researchers were studying children with communication problems. They developed tests to help diagnose the problem. In 1954, Italian researchers started testing children. They found that the brain has trouble with certain sounds and voices.

CAPD can affect people in different ways. They may have trouble finding the source of a sound. They may not be able to tell the difference between two sounds at the same time. They may not understand patterns of sound or changes in voice. They may also have trouble understanding what someone is saying.

To diagnose CAPD, doctors and specialists use tests. They observe how a person listens and responds to sounds. They may use special tools to measure how the brain works. There is no one test that works for everyone, and we do not know what causes CAPD.

A teacher can help a student with CAPD in several ways. The teacher can use visual aids, such as pictures or videos, to help the student understand what is being said. The teacher can also use simple language and repeat instructions. They can give the student extra time to understand what is being said. The teacher can also provide a quiet space for the student to work and listen.

Twelfth Night is a play that says hiding the truth can be useful in many cases. But in the end, a person must decide whether to reveal the truth or keep hiding. If they tell the truth, they may lose relationships with others. If they keep hiding, they may lose themselves.

The play also talks about people hiding their true selves by pretending to be the opposite sex. This is a big problem because it makes people ask why they do this. Why do they want to hide who they are? In the play, a character named Viola pretends to be a man to protect herself from harm. She is good at pretending and people believe she is a man. But she loses her friends and has to deal with love feelings from two people - one man and one woman.

The play shows how hiding the truth can help people find their feelings. Viola's pretending helps one man find love with her, but it also makes things complicated. The man, Orsino, had feelings for Viola when she was pretending to be a man. Now he is confused. The woman, Olivia, loves Viola when she thinks she is a man, but when she finds out, she loves Viola's twin brother, Sebastian.

The play makes people think about why people hide who they are. Is Olivia really in love with women, or does she just look at people's appearance? The play says it is not easy to know what people really feel. Olivia easily changes her feelings from one person to another. She loves Viola when she thinks Viola is a man, but when she finds out she is a woman, Olivia loves Viola's twin brother.

The German empire in Africa was known for its harsh treatment of local people. One example is the Ovaherero and Nama groups in German South West Africa. However, this is not a complete picture of the German empire. The way Germany ruled its colonies varied a lot. Even the way it provided education was different in each place. 

In 1919, Britain took control of German East Africa (now called Tanganyika). They found many Africans who were well-educated and could read and write. Germany's education efforts in other colonies, like Kamerun, were also praised by people who lived at the time. 

But South West Africa (now Namibia) was a different story. The government in East Africa built schools for local people and gave them a big role in education. In South West Africa, the job of educating the local people was left to missionary groups who got little help from the government. The government did invest in education for European people in the colony. They built schools and controlled missionary schools. 

The government's choices had a lasting effect on South West Africa. Many other German colonies had a lot of educated Africans. But in South West Africa, most people remained uneducated and unable to read. Many things caused the difference between South West Africa and other colonies. This paper will look at these things and what happened in South West Africa, especially what settlers and government officials thought about the local people.

There is a lot written about education in the German empire. Much of this writing is in German and was done a long time ago. The early writing mostly described how education was done in the different colonies. Later writing in English compared education in different colonies and looked at specific parts of education in more detail. These studies showed that each colony had a different education system. One of the most important studies is by Cohen. He compared education in South West Africa and East Africa. He said that the many European settlers in South West Africa explained many of the differences in the colony's education system.

South West Africa had a warm climate, but much of the land is desert. This is why there were a lot of European settlers in South West Africa. By 1913, about 15,000 Europeans lived there. Only about 5,300 Europeans lived in the colony with the next largest number of settlers, East Africa.

Heavy metal music is a popular music style that has grown very much over the last 100 years. Many people think it is very difficult to list all the different kinds of heavy metal music. It is even harder because many of these kinds of music have smaller groups within them. One of the most interesting kinds of heavy metal music is called heavy metal rock. It has many different emotions, mostly dark and unhappy ones. It is also very different because people started to make their own kinds of heavy metal music a long time ago. This led to smaller groups of music, and this chain of smaller groups continues today.

Today, heavy metal music is very hard to understand because it has many different kinds of music in it. But to understand it, we must first know what heavy metal music is and why it is a special kind of music.

Heavy metal music is a kind of music that is often about the darker side of life. It is music with more sound, more volume, and more energy. People who play heavy metal music are very good at playing their instruments, and you can hear this in their music. Heavy metal music also has a connection to drugs. Many people used drugs to create some of the first heavy metal music in the 1970s. This music had many strange and unusual qualities that were new to the music world. Later, other kinds of heavy metal music took some of these qualities from other kinds of music, like the Romantic Era. Some examples of heavy metal music show how dark and unhappy it can be:

These words from the song Helter Skelter show the darker side of music. They talk about the ups and downs of life, and some people think this song was one of the first heavy metal songs. It was a response to a song by the Rolling Stones that was also very heavy and dark. The Beatles wanted to show that they could make music just as heavy as the Rolling Stones.

Henri Rousseau: A Dream of Acceptance

Henri Rousseau painted a very special picture called "The Dream" in 1910. This painting shows a woman looking at wonderful things in a dream. But it also shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals as an artist. He wanted other artists and people who love art to accept and praise him. But he had a big problem. He wanted to be accepted by the art world, but he also wanted to be himself and paint in his own way.

To understand Rousseau's painting, we need to know a little about his life. He was born in 1844 in a town in northwest France. His father was a hardware seller. Rousseau did not go to school to learn about art. Instead, he worked for many years for the government. He became a toll collector and was known as a customs officer.

Rousseau's life was very sad. His wife and many of their children died. He was left with only one child, a daughter named Julia. He started painting to help him feel better and to start a new life. Rousseau was not like other artists who painted beautiful and romantic pictures of peasants. He was a folk painter who painted about the things people in his class thought about.

Rousseau wanted the art world to accept him. He started painting late in life and was working at the same time as many other famous artists. It was hard for him to get recognition. It was not until around the same time that another artist, Matisse, became famous that Rousseau started to get the recognition he wanted. A writer named Jan Gordon said that Matisse and Rousseau were different. Matisse wanted to be a good painter and not paint in a boring way. Rousseau just wanted to paint in a way that would make people accept him as an artist.

Many great thinkers believe that ethics and aesthetics are connected. They think that truth and beauty are the same. I agree with this idea. As the great poet John Keats once said, "Beauty is truth, truth beauty- That is all / Ye know on earth, and all ye need to know." We learn about many things in life through education or experience. But we seem to understand ethics and aesthetics in a different way. We try to explain what is good or beautiful, not make rules for art or behavior.

When we talk about art or morals, we can't fully describe what makes something good or beautiful. For example, we can talk about the colors, shapes, and context of a painting like the Mona Lisa. But these things don't explain why it's a great work of art. When people talk about their favorite art or literature, they often say, "There's something about it" that they can't explain.

I believe that both art and morals have a special quality that can't be fully described. As the writer Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can't be said any other way. . . . you tell a story because a statement would be inadequate." We can describe art and morals, but there's always something more.

I think that this is why ethics and aesthetics are connected. We experience both of them in a deep way that can't be fully explained. This is especially true for literature. Literature has a special ability to teach us about values and morals. As the writer McKean said, "What makes literature unique is its moral quality. It's as important to our lives as our values themselves."

Germany is a strong country with its own culture. This culture comes from many different groups of people. You can feel it in the great cities of Germany, from München near the Alps to the city of Kiel near the Baltic Sea.

Germany has a long history. Many different tribes lived in this area. They came from many places. The name 'Germany' comes from these tribes. But its meaning is not clear.

The Roman writer Tacitus said the name came from a group of people called the Tungrians. They were also called Germans before they crossed the Rhine River and fought the Gauls. The Roman leader Julius Caesar used the word 'Germanus' in his writings about the wars he fought against the Gauls. Caesar got the word from the Gauls themselves. He used it to talk about the people he had not yet defeated.

Some people think the name 'Germany' comes from a spear used by the Germans in war. Others think it comes from the Old Irish word 'garim', which means 'to shout'. This may mean the Germans were loud.

The Roman writer Tacitus wrote about the origins of the Germans in his book 'De Origine et situ Germanorum'. He said the Germans were the first people to live in the area. They did not come from other places. They were not mixed with other groups of people.

The Romans did not live in Germany. They sent soldiers to the area to get goods and to fight. But they mostly stayed in their own country. The Germanic tribes lived on the edge of the Roman Empire. They traded goods and skills with the Romans.

I looked down at the picture before me.  My mind was empty.  I was not feeling any strong feelings.  I was simply looking at the view.  My brain was working quickly.  It was taking in the picture and then moving on.  I did not have strong thoughts about what I was seeing.  I was just observing.

I once bought a book called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain."  An artist told me to buy it.  It teaches people how to draw.  One thing it says is to draw a square around a picture.  This makes it easier to understand.

I was looking at a bowl of fruit.  But I could not imagine a square around it.  I was too busy looking at all the details.  I was amazed.

Many famous artists, like Picasso and Monet, have their own ways of seeing the world.  I wanted to be an artist too.  I wanted to create something special.  I wanted to make a good picture.

My hand reached for a pencil.  I was ready to start drawing.  But then I thought about something else.  My hand went to the toilet handle.  I had to move something that was stuck.

I grabbed a mop and a piece of toilet paper.  I put the mop on the floor and stood up straight.  Then I bent down and put my hand into the toilet.  It was not easy.  But I did it.

Teenagers are dying in car accidents. Many things cause this problem. One reason is that the teen brain is not ready for the dangers of driving. Teens also do not have much experience driving. This lack of experience causes more accidents and increases the number of rollover accidents, speeding, and driving off the road. 

When teens drive with their friends, the risk of an accident is even higher. A study in Southern California found a connection between the age of passengers and the number of traffic accidents.

California and other states are trying to make driving safer for teens. They require special temporary licenses that limit the hours teens can drive and do not allow other minors as passengers. But these special licenses are just temporary solutions. The real problem is that teens, as a group, are not able to handle the risks and responsibilities of driving.

A psychologist named Marvin Zuckerman says that 18 is too young to have a regular driver's license. He found that people under 20 years old often want to take risks for the fun of it. This makes sense. We should delay giving driver's licenses to young teens until this desire for risk-taking goes away. If we continue to give licenses to young teens, we will see many more accidents and the number of deaths will be very high. 

In a few years, many more teens will be able to drive. By 2010, millions of new teen drivers will be on the road. We need laws to protect them. Schools can teach driver's education, but no one under 18 should be allowed to drive. A special permit could still be given before a regular license, and teens would still need to practice driving with an adult. The number of practice hours could be the same as in most states. For example, in California, teens need 6 hours of driving with an adult and 50 hours of practice. National laws to protect teens would be a good way to make sure all teens are safe.

This idea is not new. It is a good way to protect teens.

I looked through the films at the Library of Congress. I decided to watch all the trick films. There were fifteen of them from 1895 to 1901. These films use creative editing to create illusions. My study of film looked at how these films work and why some of them are different from others.

Most trick films at the time were made in a special setting. The camera did not move. It stayed in one place. The films used long shots and some medium shots. They did not use close-up shots. This is because of the way the films were made. The actors did not move towards or away from the camera. They only moved side to side.

One film, Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel, shows actors entering from one side and moving back and forth. The camera does not follow them when they leave the frame. This is because the films were made like plays. The actors did not move up or down. They only moved side to side.

Most tricks were short and simple. They were like magic tricks. They showed things disappearing or changing quickly. Some films were a little longer. But most were only a minute or less. They did not tell a story. They just showed a trick.

But some film makers tried something new. They joined two or more shots together to create an illusion. For example, a film of a person being beheaded is actually two shots. One shot shows the person being beheaded and another shot shows the head being removed. The viewer sees only one shot, but there are two physical shots.

John Taylor of Caroline was a strong supporter of Republicanism. He was a farmer and had a short time in politics. This made him known for his strong opinions about freedom and the government. He thought farming was the best job. He used this idea to influence his thoughts about the government. He wanted to keep and grow a good system of farming.

Taylor believed the United States had a chance to make a perfect system of government. There was no old tradition to follow. This made it easy to create a new way of governing. He believed that all people are equal and that if one person is not free, none are. He thought the government should not control people's rights. He said that in nature, strong people take control. But in a civilization, this should not happen.

Taylor wanted to make a government that knows people have good and bad inside. He thought a government should help people be good. He believed good principles are those that protect property, help farming, and stop people from being too rich. He thought a good government would work well, no matter who is in charge. He believed people are always acting in their own best interest. But if they only think of themselves, it is bad. He wanted a government to control people's bad behavior and keep them from hurting others.

Taylor wanted a small federal government. It should only have the powers the Constitution says it has. He thought a big government is expensive and could be unfair. But he also thought a simple, direct reading of the Constitution could be wrong. He believed we should understand the ideas of the people who wrote it.

Taylor thought the Declaration of Independence is the true rule of the United States. It says the country is made up of many states, not one country. This is more clear than the Constitution.

Look at Figure 17. There was a big drop in the number of people submitting their commuter logs in the third month of the project. This was a little disappointing. It is hard to know why this happened. Winter had just started at our school. Fewer people were walking or biking because of the cold weather. Many students were busy with schoolwork and preparing for grades. They may have forgotten to fill out the logs. The month of December is also a busy time of year. People have holidays and a long break from school. They do not need to come to campus. Classes started again in late January. This might be why there were few log submissions that month. However, this does not explain why there were few submissions for February. Perhaps the project got less exciting after the start. We had a lot of energy at the beginning. We created a special project, Carpool Challenge Week, to get people excited again in March. This worked and led to more log submissions. We had a problem keeping people interested, even with semester breaks and holidays. 

Another problem with the project is that people like driving their cars. This is part of our culture. We need to give people reasons to use other ways to travel. We gave prizes to people, like gift cards to local stores and restaurants. This helped. But it might have been better to give bigger prizes, like a new bicycle or a new car. This could have kept people interested in the project.

The prizes did not change for a long time. If we had given bigger prizes, it might have helped. The prizes we were giving were good at first, but bigger prizes might have kept people interested in the project.

An ETF is a special kind of investment. It is like an index fund, but it is more flexible. It trades like a stock on a stock exchange. An ETF gives you the benefits of many investments, like an index fund. It also gives you the freedom to sell short, buy more, and buy just one share at a time.

ETFs have some good things. They are not very expensive. They are also very flexible. You can trade them easily. They come in many kinds. You can choose the right one for you.

But ETFs also have some bad things. You have to pay a fee to trade them. This is like paying a fee to buy a stock. Some people think this is not good.

We will look at an ETF called IHF. We will compare it to its top 10 holdings. We want to know if it is better to buy the ETF or just the top 10 stocks. We will look at the return, or money made, and the risk, or how much money you might lose.

We will look at the 10 stocks that make up 63.58% of the ETF. We will use this information to calculate the return and risk of a portfolio made up of just these 10 stocks. This will help us understand if the ETF is a good choice.

Our results show that a portfolio of just the top 10 holdings has a higher return, or more money made, than the ETF. It also has a lower risk, or less money lost. This could be a good choice for an investor.

But we need to be careful. We need to make sure our results are correct. We will look at the standard deviation, or how much the stock's value can change, of each of the top 10 stocks. This will help us understand if the difference between the ETF and the portfolio of top 10 stocks is real or just a mistake.

Poe's poem "Dream-Land" is one of his best works. In this poem, Poe uses the word "Thulé" in lines 6 and 56. Poe got this word from the famous writer Virgil. Virgil wrote about Thulé as an island north of Britain that the Greeks thought was the end of the world.

But there is another source that Poe might have used. Poe liked German writers. There is a writer named Johann Wolfgang von Goethe who wrote a poem called "Faust". Goethe wrote "Faust" in two parts, the first part in 1808 and the second part in 1832. In the second part of "Faust", there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé". This poem is about a king whose wife dies after giving him a special cup. The king then starts drinking a lot and crying because he misses his wife. He decides it is time to die and gives all his things to his children except the cup. Then he goes to a high place, throws the cup into the water, closes his eyes, and dies.

The King of Thulé and the king in "Dream-Land" are similar. Maybe they are like two dark friends who both lost someone they loved. "Faust" was also made into a play by a man named Henry P. Grattan in 1842. This play was published just before Poe used the word Thulé in "The Pit and the Pendulum".

Poe wrote about Thulé twice in his writings. He used the phrase "ultma Thule" in "The Pit and the Pendulum" and the phrase "Thulé" in "Dream-Land". "Dream-Land" starts and ends with the word Thulé. "The King of Thulé" and "Dream-Land" can be read together. In "Dream-Land", the speaker describes a dark and lonely place. He sees dead friends and a world without color. These scenes are similar to "The King of Thulé" where the king has lost his wife and is lonely.

Goethe was a famous writer that Poe would have known. Poe said he liked another writer who liked Goethe, Alfred, Lord Tennyson. Poe would have read Goethe's work in many copies that were published after the original.

California law says a customer who is hurt after falling on applesauce in a grocery store can ask for more money as punishment. This is because the store manager knew about the spill twice and did not clean it up for 30 minutes.

A judge is not likely to throw out Jennifer Palmer's claim. To get more money as punishment, Palmer must show that the store manager acted on purpose to ignore the danger. She must also show that his actions were bad and meant to hurt people. 

Palmer can say the store manager knew that not cleaning the spill could cause harm. Many people had fallen in the store in the months before she fell. The manager still did not clean the spill. Palmer can argue that the manager's actions were very bad and meant to hurt people.

The manager, Paul Martin, was eating dinner when he was told about the spill. He said he did not have time to deal with customer complaints. Later, another employee told him about the spill again, but he said the same thing. At 5:30 pm, Palmer fell and hurt her back. Before she fell, five other people had fallen in the store that year.

California law says a person can get more money as punishment if the other person acted with "oppression, fraud or malice." Malice means the person acted on purpose to hurt someone, or they did something very bad and ignored the danger. The law says conduct is malicious when a person is aware of the danger and does not try to stop it.

In a previous case, a court said a person's actions were malicious when they ignored the danger and knew the consequences would be bad. The court said the person acted on purpose to ignore the danger.

I took a class in Islam at CBC almost four years ago.  One big question we discussed was if Islam is a hostile religion.  I think this question is even more important today.  In the years since 9/11, I have seen the media's view of Islam change from negative to very positive in America.  It is hard to imagine that a president with a Muslim family background could be elected in 2001.

The story of the Prophet Muhammad interests me.  What I know of Muhammad's history does not match his personality.  I used to think Muhammad forced people to convert to Islam.  He would conquer cities and make the people believe in Islam.  But the biography of Muhammad says he was a kind and humble man.  People came to believe in him because of his good character, not because he was powerful.

I also see some strange similarities between the jobs of Jesus and the miracles of Muhammad.  One example is when Muhammad multiplied food so there was enough for many people.  This kind of writing makes me think the writers want Muhammad to be seen as a kind and humble man who did not need to prove anything.  This is not fair because it takes away from the importance of Jesus' life and work.

There are many stories in the biography that make it seem like the writers are trying to show how people became Muslims on their own.  But some of these stories come from people who heard from other people, not from the people who actually knew Muhammad.  I do not like this because it makes the stories seem less important.

What bothers me most about this book is that it says Muhammad was a good and humble man.  But history says he was not like that.  I wonder if people today know the true story of Muhammad's rise to power.

Christianity's history is interesting.  Let's look at it.  After Jesus died, the teachings he spread were not used in the development of Christianity.  Instead, the religion moved forward in a different way.  If we look at the history of Christianity in broad strokes, we see a trend of moving away from its start.  Today, people are becoming more aware and looking for change.  Some people still follow traditional ideas, but they are not as many as those who want something new.  People who believe in Jesus' ideas will become more aware of the history of their faith in the future.  A yearning will grow to know the real ideas of Jesus and the religion he started.  It may take a long time, but this will happen.  In the future, there will be a change.  People will try to remove the things that were added to Christianity over time.  They will go back to what Jesus taught.  This will be a big change.  It will be like going back in time.  There will be a movement to get back to the ideas Jesus taught.  When this happens, the United States and Europe will be affected.  People will start to worship like Jesus taught.  The church will still be strong, but the way people think will be the same.  There will be less difference between different groups.  This is happening in history.  It happened before.  The Romans used to persecute Christians, but later they became Christian.  Our country used to be unfair to African-Americans, but now they are leaders.  Something like this will happen in the Christian religion.  It will go back to its start.  To make this happen, people will read Jesus' words in a new way.  They will not take them as facts, but as examples.

Jesus lived a long time ago.  Before him, only one main religion existed: Judaism.  It was the root of Christianity.  The Jews believed in one God and the authority of their scriptures.  When the Romans took control of Jerusalem in sixty-three B.C., the Jewish people were not all the same.  They were divided into groups like the Sadducees and Pharisees.

The Jungle is a book that shows human beings are very selfish. They want to make their lives better without thinking about others. The Jungle shows this in many ways. The owners of big factories are a good example. They only care about making their factories bigger and more successful. They do not think about anything that gets in their way or hurts anyone.

The book's writer, Upton Sinclair, describes the factories in a way that shows the damage they cause. He says the factories are very dirty and make a lot of smoke. He wants the reader to see how bad the situation is. The owners do not care about people or animals that get hurt by their factories. They do not care about the dirty water from the factories or the animals that live in the area.

The owners also do not care about their workers. They want to make money, not help their workers. They make their workers work very hard and then fire them without warning. During the time the book is set, there were no laws to protect workers. So, the owners could do what they wanted. The workers had to work in bad conditions and live in poor conditions too. They were like slaves.

The workers had no help or information to make their lives better. Some groups were formed to help workers, but they often made money off the workers instead. The workers were very unhappy and had no way to escape the bad situation. The Jungle says it is like this because the owners are very cruel and unfair.

Many authors use different ways to make readers feel a certain way about important things. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these techniques in his novel The Great Gatsby. Fitzgerald often pairs an adjective and a noun together in a way that is not usual. He uses this to give readers a feeling about a subject. He also gives meaning to a symbol and then uses it to remind readers of a feeling.

Fitzgerald uses this technique with many colors, including gold, green, white, gray, red, and pink. In The Great Gatsby, he builds up meaning for white and gray. He uses these colors to remind readers of a feeling about important objects.

Fitzgerald makes white and gray mean the same thing: all the same. White is better and more important. Gray is old and faded. He starts to use these colors in the beginning of the book. People always wear white: Daisy and Jordan wear white, Nick wears white clothes, and Tom wears a white shirt. Even the streets are white: "the white chasms of lower New York".

Fitzgerald also uses these colors to describe common things: the names of people are gray, a child is gray, and a man is gray. He does this to show that these things are not important.

After building up meaning for white and gray, Fitzgerald uses them to show that something is not important. He starts by describing Daisy in white clothes. Readers begin to see Daisy as not a person, but just something that Gatsby wants. Fitzgerald uses this technique again to show that Daisy is not important.

Fitzgerald also uses this technique with other colors, including gold, green, red, and pink. He builds up meaning for these colors and then uses them to remind readers of a feeling about important objects.

San Diego County is a good place for growing food. The weather is mild and sunny. Farmers grow many kinds of food there. These include tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, berries, honey, and peppers. Many people in the area want to buy food from local farms that do not use chemicals. This is called organic food. There is a big market for this type of food in San Diego. Many people have to wait to buy it.

Farmers who grow organic food often give tours of their farms. People can walk around, look at the plants and animals, and learn about farming. This can be a good way for farmers to make money. It can also help people understand how food is grown.

Growing organic food has some problems. It takes more work and time to remove pests and weeds and to make the soil healthy without chemicals. It is also more expensive than growing food using chemicals. A small farm cannot produce as much food as a big farm. But organic farming helps the environment. It makes the area have more plants and animals. This is good for the land, the water, and the people who live there.

The land in this story is near a town called Potrero in San Diego County, California. It is 160 acres of land with different kinds of plants and trees. It is next to a forest. Many kinds of plants and animals live there. Some are in danger of disappearing. Others are getting less common.

People have lived in this area for a long time. Before the farmers came, Native Americans lived there. Then, people raised cattle and cut down trees for wood. This land was used for farming for many years.

I chose this land to study what a farmer might do to make farming less expensive and to help the plants and animals. I found an organic farm in the same area to use as an example.

Culture is important in any talk. It is not easy to understand. A talk between people from different cultures can be difficult. To make a good agreement, it is helpful to understand a culture's values and ways. Culture is not the same for everyone. 

When we meet people from a different culture, we compare their ways to our own. We try to learn about their history and what they think is important. We do not try to change their ways. We accept them for what they are. This is especially true in talks where one side has more power.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies have their own culture too. For example, some companies work long hours. Others have a more relaxed schedule. We can see a company's culture in how its workers dress and talk. Some companies want their workers to help charities. Others do not.

Different people within a culture have different ideas. This can be true even within the same company. Some people from other cultures may seem the same but are not. We should not just look at the surface. We need to look deeper.

Understanding a culture's values is important. These values tell us why people act a certain way. If people value being polite, they will not argue in public. If people value getting a good deal, they will not give in easily. We should learn about our opponent's values before a talk. This will help us make a good agreement.

People believe in a higher power. One Bible passage says: "The fool hath said in his heart, 'There is no God.'" This is in the Christian Bible's Psalm 14. A man named St. Anselm wrote about God's existence. Another person, Thomas Aquinas, also wrote about God. Both men wanted to prove that God exists. They wrote their ideas in the same time period, so we will look at their ideas together.

Let's assume both men are right about God. This is because we are trying to compare their ideas. If we think of a different kind of higher power, it will not be fair to compare their ideas. They wrote about the same God, the one in the Bible.

We will look at St. Anselm's idea first. He said people can find God inside themselves. He said we can see that God exists in our own minds. We don't need to look outside ourselves for proof. This idea is like faith. Faith means believing something without proof. Many Christian texts say that faith is important.

St. Thomas Aquinas had a different idea. He said we can prove God exists using reason and evidence. We don't need faith. This idea is good for telling people about God. It can help people join the Christian church. They can believe in God because of logic, not just because of faith. St. Thomas said there are five logical reasons to believe in God: change, cause and effect, things that exist but could not exist, levels of perfection, and order. He said we can understand God's existence by using these ideas. We can know about God without seeing him.

A long time ago, around five hundred years before Christ, a prince was born. This prince would one day be called Buddha. He lived a long life and became enlightened. His teachings created Buddhism.

Buddhism is a very old religion. It is more than two thousand five hundred years old. It looks different today than it did when Buddha was alive. This can be seen in the country of Sri Lanka. The people there observe a special ceremony called the water-cutting ceremony.

Many people, both monks and laymen, take part in this ceremony. It has meaning, even though Buddha never taught about a celebration like this. The differences between Buddhism today and in Buddha's time are many. They can be seen in many things, from the small traditions to the main ideas of the religion.

The Buddhist community has had to change its main ideas over time. This has happened because of forces both from outside and inside the community. The community is made up of people who follow Buddha's teachings. Forces from outside the community are from people who do not believe in Buddhism.

We need to know some important words to understand what we are talking about. An internal force is a force that comes from people inside the Buddhist community. An external force is a force that comes from people outside the Buddhist community. A hostile force is a force that hurts the community. A benign force is a force that does not hurt or help the community.

We will use these words a lot in this discussion. Now, let's talk about the main ideas of Buddhism. Buddhists believe in three important things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is made up of three parts: the Tripitaka. This has many texts that explain Buddhism. The Sutta Pitaka has the Suttas. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for how to live. The Abhidhamma Pitaka has ideas about the world. These ideas include no soul, suffering in life, and that everything is changing.

By understanding these ideas, people can stop the cycle of death and rebirth. This cycle is called Sansara. It happens over and over. Along with stopping Sansara, people can also stop desire, hatred, and delusion. These are the things that come from being not enlightened. In the Vinaya Pitaka, there are rules for how to live. For people who are not monks, there are five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not behave improperly with someone of the opposite sex, and do not take drugs. For monks, there are many more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, attachment causes suffering. Third, suffering can be stopped.

Two countries, the United States and Mexico, had a long rivalry. It lasted 57 years, from 1836 to 1893. This rivalry had a big fight, the Mexican-American War of 1846-1848. The United States won and took Texas and the American Southwest.

The two countries had many other fights. They disagreed on issues like religion, culture, and tradition. They also disagreed on things they wanted like money and trade. This is like many other countries that have rivalries with their neighbors. 

When countries share a border, they often have disagreements. This can create problems between the countries. The United States and Mexico are like many other countries with long rivalries. They share a border and have had many disagreements.

One reason for the rivalry was a difference in religion. The United States and Mexico had different views on what was important. This was a big problem between the two countries. Many other countries have had disagreements over religion throughout history.

A long time ago, the English and Spanish had a disagreement. This feeling of distrust was passed down to the United States and Mexico. This made it hard for the two countries to be friends.

There were 17 fights between the United States and Mexico during their 57-year rivalry. Most of these fights were about territory and who controlled the land. There were also problems with people crossing the border and causing trouble.

As time went on, Mexico became more dependent on the United States. The United States' goals changed from wanting more land to wanting to help Mexico. This helped end the rivalry between the two countries.

Fifteen years ago I became very sick. I was a nurse at the time. I chose this job because I wanted a safe and secure life. I did not have a safe and secure life when I was a child. People said, "You will always have a job. People will always get sick." So, I chose nursing. I wanted to be a scientist or a journalist, but I chose nursing instead.

Now I am 46 years old and I am not working. I do not have much money. I get a little money from the government, but it is not enough. I get by, but it is hard every day. I am not safe or secure anymore. But I know one thing: I could not have made it without my family and a few good friends. They helped me a lot. When bad things happen, it is hard to feel strong.

My point is that bad things can happen in life. We cannot prepare for everything. Some things are too big to handle alone.

I agree that we should not put all our trust in the government. It is not strong. I think we should learn to trust each other again. We should help each other and ask for help when we need it.

The people who want to be independent say that is how America was built. But it was not just independence that helped them. They had compassion, respect for each other, and shared their resources.

So, be prepared. I have a kit with food, water, and other things I need in case of an emergency. I also have a first aid kit and a way to purify water. If you have a farm and can grow your own food, that is a good idea. But also get to know your neighbors and ask for help if you need it.

Why do living things change over time? Are there limits that affect how they change? Even a long time ago, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that scientists have not yet found a way to explain the simplest living things in a simple way. Today, scientists are using math to understand how living things grow and change. Recently, math was used to study how mollusks, a group of animals with shells, grow their shells. Our study is trying to use math to understand how living things change over time. We are using math to study how a type of mollusk called Prunum grows its shell.

To do this, we used pictures of Prunum shells to find numbers that we can use to model how the shell grows. We used a special computer program called CerioShell to create models of what the shell might look like. These models can help us understand how living things can change over time.

A shell is like a tube that grows over time. It grows around a center point, and it has lines that separate each part of the shell. We can count how many parts there are and study how they grow. We can also study how the shell grows as the animal moves through time and space.

We can use math to show how the shell grows and change over time. This can help us understand how living things change and grow. We can use this information to create new ideas about how living things change over time.

A shell can be thought of as a tube that grows in a circle. The circle is divided into parts called whorls. Each whorl is like a ring that grows around the center of the shell. The center of the shell is called the columella. The whorls grow around the columella, and a line called a suture separates each whorl. The last whorl is the biggest, and the rest of the shell is called the spire. The tip of the spire is called the apex, and the other end is called the base. The animal comes out of the shell through an opening called the aperture.

We can look at shells in different ways, such as from the top, bottom, or side. We can also count the whorls by drawing a line from the top and counting the parts. We can use math to show how the shell grows and changes over time.

We can study how the shell grows by tracing the path of the aperture. The aperture is the opening of the shell, and we can use math to show how it changes over time. This can help us understand how living things change and grow.

The number of babies and young children dying in Indonesia has not changed much in the last ten years.  Indonesia is making progress on some of the goals set for the year 2015, like providing clean water and sanitation.  But the country is not improving as quickly as it needs to on health for mothers and babies.  We will look at the reasons for this below.  They show that Indonesia needs to make its health system stronger, not just improve specific programs.

More women in Indonesia are giving birth with a trained health worker.  Now, 72% of births have a trained worker.  However, this number still includes traditional workers who cannot help if the birth is complicated.  Many mothers die because of bleeding after childbirth.  So, the progress in this area is not as good as it seems.  There are also fewer children with diarrhea who visit a health professional.  We do not have complete information on care for new mothers.  But it is clear that this is a problem.  Many areas of the country have low rates of care for new mothers.

Not enough women in Indonesia have a C-section when they need one.  Only 4% of births are C-sections.  The percentage is higher in cities, 7%, but lower in rural areas, 2%.  This shows that people in cities have better access to healthcare.  This is a problem of fairness.  Another problem is that people who are poor have a harder time getting healthcare.  There is a 27% gap in who uses healthcare services between the richest and poorest people.  The poor cannot afford to pay out of their own money for healthcare.

The next question is how to make healthcare better for babies and mothers.  The main question is how to make sure there are enough healthcare services.  Should Indonesia develop special programs or make its healthcare system better?  It is clear that special programs can solve specific problems.  They have clear goals and can give quick results.  But there are some problems with this approach.  One problem is that if we spend a lot of money on one area, we may not have enough money for other areas.  Also, many programs can make it hard to coordinate services and give too much paperwork.

Victorian novels are known for their detailed stories about people of high social class in England during that time. But two novels, Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights, are different. They use mystery and strange events to make the characters more interesting. These elements help readers understand the characters' feelings and reasons for their actions.

In Oliver Twist, the author uses strange and confusing ideas to show Oliver's feelings. For example: "He was still walking between Sikes and Crackit, who were yelling. The words they said sounded in his ears. When he finally paid attention, he found he was talking to them." Oliver is very confused and scared. The strange visions make the reader understand how Oliver feels.

The strange events in Oliver Twist often happen in Oliver's dreams. These dreams show the reader what is wrong with Oliver and what he is feeling. In chapter 28, Oliver remembers the shooting of his friend. He relives the event in his mind, like a dream. Oliver is very scared and does not know what is happening. He is also very hurt and in a lot of pain.

Oliver has no control over what happens to him. He does not try to stop the bad things that happen. The shooting in the story shows that Oliver has no control over his life. He is influenced by the people around him, like the bad man Fagin. This makes Oliver feel defeated and without hope.

Wuthering Heights is another novel that uses strange and confusing events to make the characters more interesting. The author writes: "The day passed quickly. There was no day – it was gone as soon as it started. The night was long and quiet, but it passed quickly."

I worked in an after-school program two years ago. I helped Elementary age students with their studies. I was good at English and reading. The program's instructor asked me to help a boy named Adrian. He was in third or fourth grade. He was having trouble reading. I helped him for a time, but I saw that something was not right. Some letters he read well, but others he did not understand. He spoke perfect English, but this was strange.

I asked his mother for help. She did not speak English. I spoke a little Spanish, but not much. We tried to talk, but it was hard. Then I understood the problem. Adrian could read, but he did not know the English alphabet. I hope this helped him.

I tell this story because there is a big problem in schools: the language barrier. This is a big problem in California. Even a child who speaks good English can have trouble reading. I think everyone agrees that this is a problem. So, what can we do? In Adrian's case, tutoring in English reading helped. But for children who do not speak much English, the answer is not simple. There is no one answer. We need to use many approaches.

The dual language system is a good idea. It helps children who speak Spanish, and all children. Children in bilingual programs do better in school. Many people are afraid of this idea. They think it is a waste of money. But this is not true. If we use this system in all schools, all children will benefit. How can we do this? We do not need all teachers to be bilingual. But we can have special helpers who are bilingual.

Most people are told from a young age that there is something bigger than them in the world. This idea is often taught in school or church. Some people learn about it in Sunday school, others in Temple, and some find their own answers. Many people accept the ideas of their parents. But some people reject these ideas and think there is nothing beyond what they can see and touch.

We look for answers to big questions about life. We want to know what is out there and what it means. We search for a way to understand the world. We try to find a light in the dark to guide us.

One day, my father and I sat on a porch together. It was raining and the sound of the rain was loud. He looked out into the rain and seemed to be thinking about something. He was thin and his hair was thinning. I felt sad and scared because I knew he was going to die soon.

My father died in December, a few days after my birthday. He was sick and the doctors were trying to help him, but it was not working. I did not want to watch him die. I wanted to remember him as he was, not as he was when he was sick. I thought if God was real, he would not let my father suffer. I did not say any prayers.

I did not want to see my father die. I curled up in a ball in my bed for three days. No one called me to tell me the news.

The Gothic Novel is a strange name for a story about old and new ideas. Ian Watt says it is like an "oxymoron" - two things that do not mix. People have criticized the Gothic mode for not being deep, and also praised it for its powerful and exciting parts. 

The first Gothic Novel was "The Castle of Otranto" by Horace Walpole. He used old ideas from "ancient" romances and new ideas from modern novels to create the Gothic style. He mixed old theatrical elements with new ways of writing to make a new kind of story. 

The Gothic style uses many old ideas from medieval times, like old buildings and old traditions. Even when "The Castle of Otranto" was first published, the word "gothic" was used to describe many things, like old peoples and old styles. It was seen as old-fashioned compared to new ideas in society and literature.

The mix of old and new ideas is what makes the Gothic style interesting. It stays interesting for a long time, even if the reader is far from the time when it was written. 

One of the most important ideas in Gothic stories is chivalry. Chivalry is the idea of training a good knight. It was important to Gothic writers because it represented a perfect knight who was brave, honorable, and good. They saw that society was not living up to this ideal, and they wanted to change it. 

The idea of chivalry was used in "The Castle of Otranto" to make the past seem better than the present. This was a way of saying that society had lost something important. The writer, Horace Walpole, was writing during a difficult time in history. He was unhappy with the way society was going, and he wanted to make people think about what was important. 

One character in the story, Frederic, is a good example of a chivalric knight. He is a prince who has been through hard times and is a good person. His description in the story includes many traditional ideas about chivalry, like being a gallant and courteous knight.

Supply Chain Management
------------------------

Supply chain management is the process of moving goods from the customer order to the customer. It includes the stages of raw materials, supply, production, and distribution. The term supply chain management was first used in 1982 by a consultant named Keith Oliver. He described the process of planning, implementing, and controlling the supply chain to satisfy customers quickly and efficiently.

There are six main parts of a supply chain: production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these parts to provide good customer service.

Production is the first step in the supply chain. It is the base of the whole process. Managers must know what customers want. They look at the market to understand what customers need. The market is a good guide to decide what customers demand. Managers decide what products to make and how many. They also choose where to make the products, considering customer demand and satisfaction.

The next step is to plan workloads and maintenance. Production is a very important part. Every detail matters. If details are not planned correctly, it can cost a company time and money.

Supply is the second key part of the supply chain. It includes making strategic decisions about a company's capabilities and partnerships. A company may have many divisions for a single product. Managers decide which division is best for each process. They may also outsource work to other companies to save time and money.

Inventory is the third key part. It includes storing and managing goods before they are sold. Location is the fourth part. It includes choosing the best place to make and store products. Transportation is the fifth part. It includes moving goods from one place to another. Information is the sixth part. It includes sharing information between companies and customers.

Managers use these six parts to provide good customer service. They make sure the right products are made, stored, and delivered to customers on time. This helps a company be successful.

There is a message in Burma. It says Hitler is alive.

Ellen Page, the actress from the movie Juno, stands alone on the street with a piece of cardboard. She holds it up, and the message is written on it in black. Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. It is ruled by a group of military leaders who took power in 1962. They did not win power through an election.

In 2007, people on the street began to protest. This was the first time people had protested in ten years. The protests were led by monks. The monks wore yellow robes. After the first protests, more and more people joined in. The government was not happy. The government did not want people to protest.

The government allowed the monks to meet peacefully, but then the situation became violent. The military attacked the monks and their monasteries. Foreign journalists were arrested. One journalist was killed while he was reporting on the protests.

This is not the only time that a government has tried to stop people from speaking out against it. Many governments throughout history have tried to stop people from protesting. In ancient Rome, the emperor thought they were chosen by the gods to rule. In Japan, the emperor is thought to be a god. In the United States, the president had meetings with a man who leads a group that is against freedom.

There are many examples of governments hurting their own people. In 1989, people in China protested against their government. The government did not like this, and many people were killed. In Rwanda, a group of people killed anyone who was not like them. Germany, under Hitler, killed many Jewish people.

These are just a few examples. Governments have been hurting their own people for a long time.

Duke Ellington was a famous jazz musician. He lived a long life, which helped him create many new and important works of music for his orchestra. In many of his compositions, Ellington's piano playing is not very loud. However, as a composer, he was very good at making music that showed each member of the band. He created a framework for band members to play with freedom. Ellington also wrote music that was tightly organized and used the special style of each band member to show musical ideas. This created a new and original sound for each piece.

Ellington was very good at understanding how to make each band member sound good. He knew how to make the band sound good together as a group. This skill allowed him to write some of the most innovative and great music in jazz history.

In his music, Ellington often used the voice to add a new sound to his music. This is shown in his song "Creole Love Call." In this song, he used the voice as a musical instrument. It was one of the first times he did this in his career. The song is a slow, twelve-bar blues that has six parts. Each part is different.

Part 1: The song starts with a call and response between the voice and the reeds. The voice starts with a smooth sound and then becomes rougher at the end.
Part 2: A muted trumpet player plays a solo. The solo makes the melody more interesting and uses many blue notes.
Part 3: A clarinet player plays a fast, high solo while the piano plays a subtle rhythm.
Part 4: The whole band plays like the first part, with a call and response between the brass and reed sections.
Part 5: The reeds start the call and response in a high voice. The brass and rhythm sections play a strong, rhythmic pattern.
Part 6: The song returns to the first part, with a call and response between the voice and the reeds. In this part, the voice sounds like a musical instrument.

In another song, "Hot and Bothered," Ellington uses his skill at making tight music with his band. He also uses his ear to make new and interesting sounds. In this song, a trumpet player and a singer use their voices to create a rich sound.

In "It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing)," Ellington uses a trombone player to make the melody sound new and interesting.

She always felt something was missing. She didn't know what it was. This feeling started when she was 14 years old. She was still a teenager. Three years later, at 17, she was still feeling this way. She wanted something, but not a thing. She wanted a person. But she was not interested in any boy. Some boys liked her, but she did not like them. She often thought about what could be causing this. She thought about it for a long time, but she did not know the answer.

Her home life was usually peaceful. Her parents were calm and nice people. They did not argue. They were not angry with her. They were concerned about her independence. She was different from them. She was outgoing and fun. They liked her.

But today was not a peaceful day. She walked around the house, looking for something new. She heard her mother cry out from the kitchen. She ran to the kitchen. Her mother was on the floor, hurting. "Mom, what's wrong?" she asked. Her mother said, "Ow... sweetie, I need you to take me to the hospital." The daughter helped her mother get up and drove her to the hospital.

The hospital smelled like medicine and sickness. She was not worried. She was worried about her mother. She helped her mother get a roll bed and sat with her until the doctors came. They took her mother to see a doctor. The daughter was worried.

Her mother fell off a step stool trying to get a vase from a high cabinet.

This study looked at how following a "Mediterranean Diet" affects the risk of heart disease and stroke. The study found that eating a diet high in plant foods, like fruits, nuts, whole grains, and legumes, and low in animal products and saturated fats, can reduce this risk.

Previous studies have shown that eating a Mediterranean-style diet can help people live longer and prevent heart disease. However, this study focused on the connection between the diet and stroke.

The study looked at 74,886 women, aged 38 to 63, who did not have heart disease or diabetes. The women were part of a larger study of nurses in 11 US states. The researchers asked the women about their eating habits six times between 1984 and 2004. They found that women who ate a Mediterranean-style diet had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke.

To make sure the results were accurate, the researchers looked at medical records, autopsy reports, and death certificates to confirm cases of heart disease and stroke. They also accounted for other factors that could affect the results, such as age, smoking, and physical activity.

The study found that women who ate a Mediterranean-style diet had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke. In fact, women who ate the most Mediterranean-style foods were 29% less likely to have a heart attack or stroke than those who ate the least.

This study shows that eating a Mediterranean-style diet can be an effective way to reduce the risk of heart disease and stroke. This diet is not only good for the heart, but it may also help people live longer and healthier lives.

The United States had a big financial crisis in 2007. Many people lost their jobs, the housing market fell, and some big companies were in trouble. This problem is still a problem today. So, we must ask: how did this problem happen and how can we stop it? The financial crisis happened because of bad and foolish decisions made by politicians. They pushed banks and companies to give loans to people who could not pay them back. The banks and companies then sold these loans to other places, like Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac. These companies mixed the loans together and sold them to others. When the people who borrowed the money could not pay, the banks and companies were in trouble. 

This problem began in 1999. President Clinton wanted a second term in office. He wanted to be popular. So, he made it easier for banks to give loans to people who could not afford them. A reporter at the New York Times reported in 1999, "Fannie Mae was under pressure from the government to give loans to people who earn little money. The company wanted to grow and make more money." The reporter said this could cause big problems if the economy slowed down. And it did. 

Some new kinds of loans were used to buy homes. These loans had rates that could change, and they were complicated. They were mixed together and sold to many people. This made many people borrow too much money. When the housing market fell, they could not pay back the money. The big banks and companies that bought these loans were in trouble. They lost $4.1 trillion dollars in 2007. This is a big number. It is one-third of the country's total money. Some companies were sold, and some were forced to change the way they work. Fannie and Freddie had $5 trillion dollars in loans and were taken over by the government in 2008.

Exposition: The Unwanted Guest

Exposition is that part in your story where you show your writing skills.  But not in a good way. It's like a guest that you don't want to invite to your party.

We already know the rule: "Show, don't tell."  But Dr. Merlin still makes mistakes.  She writes a lot of words that tell the reader what happened.  And it makes the reader bored.

Exposition is when you tell the reader about the story.  It's like a character telling another character a lot of information.  But your readers don't want to hear it.  They want to see it.

Let's look at an example.  You read a story and you learn that a woman met her husband a long time ago.  They got married in a big ceremony.  And then he died in front of her.  But you don't want to read about all of it happening in a few lines.  You want to see the husband's character.  You want to see how much he loved her.  And you want to see how much she loved him.

If the story tells you that she was happy with him, you want to see it in her words and actions.  You want to see her smile when she thinks of him.  You want to see her cry when she remembers him.  That way, you can feel her sadness.  And you can feel her love for him.

So, as a writer, you need to give the reader more.  You need to show, not tell.  Don't make your readers fall asleep or click the "Back" button.  Give them meat on the bone.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was live this morning (August 13, 2011) on NBC 4. The main story was about a man named Shad Hostettler. He stabbed his wife many times in Ashley, Ohio. He was arrested. The news showed his picture. He looked very bad. The news was only two minutes long. I think it was enough time.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers. He was 18 years old. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He was critically hurt. Police did not have any suspects. A special police team was working on the case. I thought this story was short. I think it was because the man who was shot was black and from a black neighborhood. I have noticed that the news does not give as much attention to minorities who are victims of crimes. If a white person is a victim, the news talks about it a lot.

The next story was about a gun hole in a helicopter. It was a .22 caliber bullet that hit the helicopter. Police want people to tell them who did it. They will give a reward of five thousand dollars to anyone who helps.

The next story was about rain and thunderstorms on Saturday afternoon. The temperature would be in the mid to low eighties. The news did not talk about this for very long.

They also talked about a robbery at a store on Clime Road in Columbus. A black man robbed the store. He wore a black sweatshirt. He was about six feet tall and weighed one hundred and fifty pounds. I thought the news talked about this man being black a lot.

Another story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big drug seller in Texas. He was in a group that sold marijuana in Ohio from Texas. He was sentenced to 300 months in prison. The news also said he was Hispanic. I did not think this was important to the story.

There is a special friendship between brothers. It is a strong and unbreakable bond. This friendship has many feelings: love, pride, jealousy, and cruelty. Brothers understand each other more than anyone else. They see themselves in each other. In hard times, this bond is clear. It can be good or bad. When these feelings are clear, they make a big difference. Part of understanding brotherly love is dealing with the problems it causes. When you look at your brother, you see yourself. You see the good and the bad. Your actions and what happens because of them show who you really are. The story "The Scarlet Ibis" shows this. Two brothers go on a difficult journey. They have many strong feelings. In the end, one brother survives, but the other does not. The story shows how one of the brothers feels proud and resentful towards his brother. The brother wants a brother he can play with and teach things to. But his brother is very sick and cannot do these things. The brother is very sad and angry. He even thought about hurting his brother. But when his brother smiles, he feels happy and loving. This shows that he cares about his brother. This is a complex feeling that shows the love and anger of brotherhood.

The main character's actions are driven by one main feeling: pride. He wants a brother who can play with him and learn from him. He wants a brother who can run and climb with him. But his brother is very sick and cannot do these things. The brother is very sad and angry that his brother cannot be the brother he wants. This is shown when he thinks about hurting his brother. But when his brother smiles, he feels happy and loving. This shows that he cares about his brother and loves him.

The human brain is a very complicated system. It helps us think and learn. As technology has improved, people have used different ideas to explain how the brain works. They compared it to a tablet made of wax, then to a piece of paper, and now to a computer. These ideas are useful, but they have limits. They can also lead to mistakes.

The brain gets information from our senses. These are like special helpers that turn what we see, hear, touch, and taste into signals. The brain uses these signals to make decisions. It does this in two parts: bottom-up and top-down. 

Imagine you see a picture of a black box on a white background. The bottom-up process looks at the picture and says, "I see some black and white colors, and some lines that mean this is a box." The top-down process uses this information to say, "I know this is a box, not a hole in the white background." 

When the brain gets information, it decides how important it is. This helps choose what we pay attention to. For example, we might see many blades of grass, but we only notice a few. We might also hear our name in a noisy room.

The brain stores information in three types: sensory, working, and long-term. We get sensory information from our senses. Working memory stores information for a short time, like 20 seconds. Long-term memory keeps information for a long time. Scientists think that working memory is like a short signal that goes through some brain cells. Long-term memory is like a special kind of protein that keeps the information.

There are many theories about how we organize our knowledge in the brain. Some ideas come from how people remember things, some come from computer science, and some come from studying the brain. One idea is that our brain has small places that connect to each other. These places are like concepts, and they connect to each other because they are related. For example, our brain might connect the idea of a "chair" to the idea of a "table," which is connected to the idea of "wooden," and so on.

The writer Aldous Huxley criticizes the dangers of new technology and the way it is supported by the system of capitalism. In his novel Brave New World, he pictures a bad future where people value groups over individuals and seek happiness right away. People are taught from a young age to choose pleasure above all else. The citizens are shown to be controlled by a single system, ruled by a powerful leader called the World Controller. 

If we look at the book through the ideas of Marxism, we can see that the writer is warning us about the problems of the economy of his time. Huxley uses special words from Marxism, such as the idea of equality for everyone being the same, and how people are controlled by the rules of society.

Huxley makes fun of capitalism in the book by showing how the common people are not aware of their relationship with the more powerful people in society. They are only interested in getting richer and more things. This is because the system is designed to keep them from knowing the truth. The people in the book, like the Delta and Gamma classes, do not have their own ideas. They are forced to follow the rules and buy things they do not need.

The wealthy people in the book are in control and do nothing to change the system. The interactions between the different people in the book show that they are very unkind to each other. They do not really know each other, and they do not care about each other's feelings. The writer may be saying that the rise of new technology and capitalism takes away people's freedom and ability to express themselves.

The people in the book do not have real love or deep feelings. They are only interested in looking good and having fun. The way the people in the different classes accept their place in society shows how the system of capitalism affects people's lives. They are happy to obey the rules and stay in line with what is expected of them.

I have been a student at University Park for two and a half years. It can be hard for students to get around campus. My first year, I lived in a dorm in East Halls. It is far from many buildings, including the Willard building. It takes me 25 minutes to walk from my home to classes in Willard when the weather is bad. I talked to an older student and learned that the East Halls were once separated from the rest of the school by empty land. Now, that space has buildings, sports fields and apartments. As the campus grows, it gets harder to get from one place to another. A good solution is the bicycle. But students must ride them and the campus needs to help.

I talked to a friend who rides a bike. He said, "Bikes are great. They are the best way to get around." Bicycles are good for your body. They are also the fastest way to travel. A simple breakfast and some exercise will take you 30 miles or more. I live off campus, far from the center of campus. The smartest thing I did was buy a bike. I ride to Thomas building for class. It takes me 5 minutes if I pedal fast. The problem is, Pollock Road is not an easy road to ride on.

There are good things about walking too. But I am too busy to walk. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk. Walking to Thomas every day would take 30-40 minutes. That is two and a half hours every week. I don't have time for that.
